## 🏗️ Architecture

```text
frontend/ React + Vite
  ├─ Scan console
  ├─ Live progress UI
  ├─ Results dashboard
  ├─ Attack-chain visualization
  └─ Auto-PR panel

backend/ FastAPI
  ├─ API routes
  ├─ Scan pipeline orchestrator
  ├─ Code scanners
  ├─ Web scanners
  ├─ AI severity + attack-chain agents
  ├─ Fix generation agents
  ├─ Auto-PR engine
  └─ SQLite persistence
```

